The paper discusses the use of quantitative phase imaging (QPI) and artificial intelligence (AI) in biomedical applications, specifically using deep learning techniques. This suggests that the paper could fall under several arXiv CS sub-categories, including computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), information theory (cs.IT), multimedia (cs.MM), and neural and evolutionary computing (cs.NE).
